Note Taking App 

1) Extract .zip file
2) Open folder in terminal
3) After step 1, run "npm install" command in terminal to install all dependencies in package.json
3) Run "npm start" in terminal
4) This app will be running on port 3000. Copy and paste the following adress in your browser "http://localhost:3000/"

To Add Note:

1) Insert a note in field.
2) Press Add button or Enter key

Note: Please, do not repeat text


To Edit Note:

1) Click over note text you want to edit
2) Note text will be on input
3) Edit
4) Press Edit button

To Remove Note:

1) Click over note text you want to remove
2) Note text will be on input
3) Press Remove button

To Change color

1) Click over note text you want to change color
2) Note text will be on input
3) Select color from Color Table, clicking over colour you want
4) Selected color will change
5) Press Change Color
6) Press Empty Field





